room_title: Escape room "The Hotel Suite" by Escape It in Baltimore
review: We celebrated our daughter’s 12th birthday by escaping from The Suite. Everyone had a blast! We’ll be back for sure!

room_title: Escape room "The Hotel Suite" by Escape It in Baltimore
review: What a fun time. We did the hotel suite escape room. We had no idea what to expect before going but had such a great time. The staff was very welcoming and helpful. I cannot wait to return to try another room.

room_title: Escape room "The Hotel Suite" by Escape It in Baltimore
review: This was my first time and I had so much fun! I loved everything about my experience at Escape It. My bestie and I played in the Suite. The clues and puzzles were well thought out. I would absolutely recommend Escape It to anyone curious about Escape rooms and want to try something new.

room_title: Escape room "The Hotel Suite" by Escape It in Baltimore
review: We absolutely loved Escape It. We did the Hotel room. We have been to a lot of escape rooms in Baltimore and this one is personally the best! We were trying to book another one right afterwards!

room_title: Escape room "The Hotel Suite" by Escape It in Baltimore
review: My husband and I wanted to try something new and different so we checked out Escape It. I found a great deal on Groupon so we decided to try the Hotel Suite. We ended up being put with a group of 8 people which could sometimes get a little chaotic but we managed to work together and got out of the room with only 6 minutes left! We had such a great time! As soon as we left I looked at him and said, "When are we going back?"
